flowRoot.flowPara: A tool that adapts to your needs, instead of trying to fit your needs into multiple different tools.
Your old tools are like salads on a menu, and you have to choose among the fixed set of options it provides.
WishSalad, however, is like a salad bar with the ingredients from the menu salads and more, and you can combine them any way you wish.
But adapting to your needs it's not only to integrate features from your old tools into a single workflow, it's also to give you control over them and your data.
Ensuring that you can still access and use it in the future, even if the services and applications you currently use are not available anymore.
And giving you control over your privacy. So that you don't have to choose between privacy and convenience.
